 $8,568,600, and cir\nculation increased $1,077,000.\nThe proportion of reserves to liabili\nties is now 23.1 per cent.\nTEE Beginning of of\nhe New Year\nShould find you resolved to start an\naccount in our Savings Dept., where\nyour deposits will earn interest\n\u2014And have national bank pro.\ntun rom 6 vy\nto\nTHE TRADERS\nNATIONAL BANK, torsr.\nBid. Asked.\nPA Ave\nALASKA COPPERS\nDUDLEY A. TYNG CO.\n184 La Salle St.\nChicago.\nHubbard-Elliott\nLaTouche Lat.\nGalena Ba\nKnights Bad Copper,\nRuifiits 1s] Island Consol,\nbought and sold.\nTirathation Soutsnet x8.\ntren, Wo priyate A Ey ou\npanics groun\nStart the New Year\nWith a Bank Account\nThe surest way to have a dollar\nis to save it. Start now with $1.00.\nWe pay 3 per cent on all savings\nBOLE. Open Saturday between\n6 and 9 p. m.\nMerchants and Mechanics\nSavings Bank\n7th and G Streets N.W,\nUnder Supervision U. 8. Treasury.\nThe Safest Investments\nAre those that do not fuctuate duriag dis.\nrurbad ondiuon, of the\noats. deed\nmor gages). ws well secured on real estate ia\nct of Columbia. comstitute \u201c\u2018giis\nedge\u2019 Investments They do not ue\ninvestments.\"\nthe fnancial responsibility of fads\nSwartzell. Rheem\nHensey Co.\n$16 F St. N. W.\nLapiiald, \u00ab1,00, 00, OSUrpius, 91,200,000,\nee\nRIGGS 3%\nIssues drafts direct, available\nthroughout the world,\nIssues letters of credit.\nBuys and sells exchange.\nTransmits money by cable.\nMakes investments for customers.\nMakes collections for customers.\nBuys and selis stocks and honds.\n2 SPECIAL DEPT. FOR LADIES\nPa. Ave. Opp. U. S. Treasury\nAMERICAN\nNATICNAL\nBANK\n1315-1317F St. Kw.\n\nGovernment\nDepositary\u2014\nDepositary nn\nBankruptey\u2014\nInterest paid\non Savings De\nposits\u2014\nSafe Deposit\nBoxes for rent.\nLetters of\nCredit\u2014\nForeign Ex\nchange.\nDon\u2019t let this year go by\nwithout starting a savings ac\ncount. We pay 3 per cent in\nterest.\nFed >a 3\n\n8\n+1\n\n\nHome Savings Bank,\n\n\nseventh and Mass. Ave.